Game details

Moto X3m 3 was not the first bike game from Mad Puffers. However, it was the best early one because it used newer technologies and released with mobile support. The previous games were good but didn 't hold up, then this game showed the community how good HTML5 bike games could get. The Moto X3m series has continued to produce new and more insane levels ever since.

Category: Driving Games
Developer: Mad Puffers
